h3.div: The drop-down menus, above, provide links to every teacher and course, including service providers and counselors. The site will be updated regularly, so we encourage you to visit at least once per week.

Teacher contact information can be found on each course page. If you have questions or concerns about the material or your child’s progress, please contact the teacher directly. They will be checking email regularly throughout this time. If you are unable to reach the teacher, please contact the building principal for assistance.

Some teachers have provided schedules or timelines as guidance, but we understand that each family's situation is unique. Please do what is best for your family and know that we are here to help as much as possible. Again, if you have questions or concerns, please reach out to your child’s teacher.
For technology and other help, go to this page.

We encourage you to visit this site regularly as updates become available. Any schedules or timelines are intended to provide support and guidance, but we understand that each family's situation is unique. Students will not be penalized for inability to complete any of the assignments contained on or linked to this site.
